25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 27, Chapter 15, Subchapter 3, is
26 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
27 27-15-318. Pregnancy Parking Act — Temporary special certificate
28 during and after pregnancy.
29 (a) This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Pregnancy Parking
30 Act".
31 (b) A woman who is pregnant, as determined by a licensed physician,
32 may apply to the Office of Motor Vehicle for a temporary person-with-a-
33 disability special certificate.
34 (c) The temporary special certificate shall:
35 (1) Conform to the requirements under § 27-15-304(a)-(c); and
36 (2) Expire one (1) year following the date the pregnant woman
